Last question then. What feelings do you carry in 
your heart for Texas A&M? One of great love and

08:51.458 --> 08:53.922
devotion. You know, it's similar to my feelings 
for my church and my family. As a matter of fact, I

09:04.419 --> 09:13.593
have planned my own funeral, and in the funeral 
I've asked that certain things be played. Amazing

09:14.114 --> 09:15.156
grace. Here I am, Lord. And the Aggie War Hymn, I've 
asked them to play that. Let's quit on that. Tell me

