about any of the conversations you remember of the 
former student officers about co-education and

09:26.975 --> 09:39.876
non-compulsory core before you resigned as 
president. Well, the reason I resigned was to run

09:40.767 --> 09:46.213
for governor. But had the former student 
leadership talked about those topics yet?

09:56.103 --> 09:56.804
Well, let's see. Well,

