actually, I remember I remember Wofford Cain, who 
was on the Development Fund Board,

10:04.932 --> 10:18.592
he was very much opposed to admitting women. And 
actually, most of my classmates were opposed to

10:19.313 --> 10:27.746
admitting women, just in talking to them. I don't 
remember the But I think as I told you, John Lindsay

10:33.367 --> 10:44.912
told me that he would never forgive me because when 
I resigned to run for governor, he became the

