10:45.466 --> 10:55.040
to admit women. And John said, what? He said, make a 
motion, John. Did you know that that was coming up

11:00.549 --> 11:02.892
when you? No, I didn't. I didn't know that. So the 
board, the association board had not discussed

11:05.797 --> 11:08.901
that? No, they didn't know that. And John said that 
He made the motion, and he said, all in favor say

11:13.529 --> 11:22.479
aye, and there were only two or three ayes. All 
opposed say no, and there was a thunderous number

