of noes. And he hit the gavel and said, the ayes have 
it. And that's how women were admitted to A&M. And

11:35.373 --> 11:39.537
as I understand it, then they went down the 
hallway. and told the, they were then called

11:39.736 --> 11:48.185
directors, now regents, that the former student 
had adopted that. I see. I didn't know that. That's

11:50.067 --> 11:53.450
what I understood that they did. But this had not 
been a subject of big discussion. No, it hadn't at

11:57.594 --> 11:59.436
that time. You know, there was not planned 
anything, but people were, most of the people I

11:59.596 --> 12:08.005
knew were opposed to it.

